snippet.textDisplay: Wow! Thank you Coke Studio Bharat for putting out folk our there. I'm a Kashmiri Pandit living in exile and preserving our language and our music is very dear to us. This feels so special to have the Wanvun integrated in this beautiful song by Mohammad Muneem featuring the incredible Noor Sahab and my dear friend Aashima. Love this. So well done. It's been a dream to have Kashmiri music represented in Coke Studio Bharat/India. Would love to connect to the team to share my ideas and concepts on Kashmiri music for the next season. 🙏
snippet.textOriginal: Wow! Thank you Coke Studio Bharat for putting out folk our there. I'm a Kashmiri Pandit living in exile and preserving our language and our music is very dear to us. This feels so special to have the Wanvun integrated in this beautiful song by Mohammad Muneem featuring the incredible Noor Sahab and my dear friend Aashima. Love this. So well done. It's been a dream to have Kashmiri music represented in Coke Studio Bharat/India. Would love to connect to the team to share my ideas and concepts on Kashmiri music for the next season. 🙏
